#34;line&#34;&gt;SADD key member [member ...]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;summary: &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;Add&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;one&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;or&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;more&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;members&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;set&lt;/span&gt;（向集合中添加一个或多个成员）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;since&lt;/span&gt;: 1.0.0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;SCARD&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;summary&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;Get&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;of&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;members&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;set&lt;/span&gt;（获取一个集合中的成员数）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;since&lt;/span&gt;: 1.0.0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;funct